                     <h2 style="font-size: 25px;text-align: center;">About Us</h2>
                     
                     <hr >
                      <p style="text-align: ;font-size: 16px;">Tathagat Gautam Buddh Government Polytechnic Shravasti was established in the year 2010.It is situated on Bahraich Bhinga Tulshipur road nearly 22 kms from district headquarters Bhinga Shravasti.Today it houses in its 5 acre campus,a main building,students hostels,library,classrooms for various faculties including Computer Science and Engineering,Electrical Engineering and Electronics Engineering.
            It's aim is to become one of the best Polytechnic College in U.P.
            <br>
The college is affiliated to the Board of Technical Education U.P.(BTE UP) and approved by All India Council of Technical Education(AICTE).It has the capacity to groom 192 students in various engineering fields every year.Over the last four years,
the institute has produced more than 100 diploma engineers in various disciples,has won several awards in academics as well as socio cultural activities and on the whole has succeeded in contributing humlbe positive efforts towards the building of a progressive society.Institute has one boy's hostel with sixty beds available and one girl's hostel which is under construction.

